 gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-950/30 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800\"><span data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"iconify i-mdi:refresh text-xl text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"text-sm text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200\"><p data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"font-medium mb-1\">Reset Progress Anytime</p><p data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"leading-relaxed\"> Need a fresh start? You can now reset your progress at any level—chapter, topic, subject! </p></div></div></div></div><div data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-950/30 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800\"><span data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"iconify i-mdi:alert-circle-outline text-xl text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"text-sm text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200\"><p data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"font-medium mb-1\">Note about your existing progress:</p><p data-v-479831c5=\"\" class=\"leading-relaxed\"> As we transition from chapter-level to question-level tracking, you may notice some discrepancies in your progress data. This is because the previous system didn't log individual question attempts as comprehensively. Going forward, all your progress will be accurately tracked at the question level. </p></div></div></div>",
